Brief Summary: I am a graduated of Johnson & Wales Bachelors of Science program for Culinary Nutrition.  Today I will be evaluating amberlynn reid's recent grocery haul.  I give some info on what I can make food wise and some tips and tricks on how to improve eating habits.  I hope amberlynn takes this advice and if she has more questions she can reach out to me.  Special thanks to Repzion since his footage is what I found for amberlynn diet.  Also special shout out to Leah Rose for suggesting this topic!  If you liked this video be sure to give it a like, leave a comment below, and don't forget to subscribe!  Thank you for watching!
